'''''Star Wars Insider'' 87''' is the 87th issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'', released in April [[2006]].

==Contents==
===Features===
*"[[Order 66: Destroy All Jedi]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>Our Bothan spies have retrieved official documents from the desk of Emperor Palpatine detailing the results of Order 66. With heavy heart, we present them to you...</small>
*"[[New Force Rising]]" {{C|by [[Frank Parisi]]}}
*:<small>We jump a hundred years into the future of ''Star Wars'' to talk with [[John Ostrander]] about new times, new challenges, and making a galaxy far, far away dangerous again&mdash;in the new series, ''[[Star Wars: Legacy]]''.</small>
*"[[Setting the Scene: Jonathan Harb Leads ILM's Digimatte Artists into Brave New Worlds]]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]]}}
*:<small>In the second installment of the ILM 30th anniversary series, ''Insider'' takes a look at the some of the jaw-dropping work done by ILM's digimatte department.</small>
*"[[Odds]]" {{C|by [[Karen Traviss]]}}
*:<small>When conducting a routine sabotage mission, members of Omega Squad discover threads that could unravel the galaxy's biggest conspiracy.</small>

===Departments===
*"[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]"
